{
  "texts": [
    "Currently, our total response time is up to 5 s, and we aim to reduce this to under 1 s. Technical pillarsIn this section, we introduce the implemented architecture of IACH and the detailed methodologies employed for each component of our system, encompassing text-to-gloss search, gloss-to-text recognition, sign language detection, and gloss correction.",
    "Software scopeOur IACH APP is a cross-platform solution, supporting both Android and iOS.",
    "The choice of programming languages for client-side development varies according to the platforms: Swift is utilised for iOS, while Kotlin is used for Android.",
    "On the server side, we use Django, a Python web framework, and MySQL database hosted on AWS cloud servers.",
    "Our database contains over 6000 text words and 5000 sign videos."
  ]
}